          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Each key in this dictionary is one of the constants listed in "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "Particle Property Keys"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and the value for each key is a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlepropertycontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object responsible for varying that property over time. Use particle property controllers to add efficient animations that change the appearance or behavior of each particle emitted by the system."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To add more complex behavior that cannot be described by a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlepropertycontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object, use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/scenekit/scnparticlesystem/1522635-addmodifierforproperties"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to add a particle modifier block. However, be aware that particle modifier blocks can severely impact rendering performance."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
